  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Proposed project site, The Sundarbans coastal region is climatically vulnerable due to its&apos; geographic location. People of this region haven&apos;t sufficient knowledge on how to reduce disaster risk, minimize loss and damage and adapt with changed climate. This project aims at improving capacity of the target communities on disaster risk assessment, signaling, pre, during and post disaster activities, adaptation techniques etc. using BEDS working experience and existing facilities.</narrative>
  </description>
